    <briefdescription>
<para>The initial attachments to create the <ref refid="classDali_1_1FrameBuffer" kindref="compound">FrameBuffer</ref> with. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><simplesect kind="note"><para>The color attachment can also be created on calling <ref refid="classDali_1_1FrameBuffer_1a147df2d3ddecc939967f1d90221d0ad7" kindref="member">AttachColorTexture()</ref>. </para>
</simplesect>
<simplesect kind="note"><para>With &quot;NONE&quot;, no attachments are created initially. However color attachments can still be added as described above.</para>
</simplesect>
@SINCE_1_1.45 </para>
